sleep under that big sky

4
00:00:17,559 --> 00:00:21,271
aren't activities,
but a way of life.

5
00:00:21,313 --> 00:00:24,232
It was between here
and those mountains

6
00:00:24,274 --> 00:00:28,737
that Cheyenne and Crow
battle took place.

7
00:00:28,779 --> 00:00:30,239
But I like it.

8
00:00:30,240 --> 00:00:31,699
It's very peaceful, huh?

9
