before Stream Access,

222
00:10:29,504 --> 00:10:32,757
we seldom required somebody to
have permission if they just

223
00:10:32,758 --> 00:10:33,508
behaved themselves.

224
00:10:33,550 --> 00:10:36,677
After Stream Access is
when the outfitters

225
00:10:36,719 --> 00:10:39,973
came into the world, not because
we wanted to make money,

226
00:10:40,014 --> 00:10:43,268
but we wanted somebody there
patrolling and policing it.

227
00:10:43,310 --> 00:10:45,103
The outfitters take care of it.

228
00:10:45,145 --> 00:10:47,307
A small stream like this can
only take so much pressure.

229
00:10:47,314 --> 00:10:48,336
It really can.

230
00:10:48,337 --> 00:10:50,691
And so we try to manage
it, fish it responsibly.

231
00:10:50,733 --> 00:10:53,278
And if somebody wants to walk
all the way from the Smith

232
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:56,427
five miles up to here,
and do it legally, I say

233
00:10:56,428 --> 00:10:57,698
all the more power to them.

234
00:10:57,740 --> 00:10:59,700
That's what I'm saying.

235
